room_title: Escape room "The Baker Street Mystery" by Cipher Escape in Morrisville
review: Had a great time in the Baker Street room! The staff were awesome and the puzzles were entertaining. And we escaped!

room_title: Escape room "The Baker Street Mystery" by Cipher Escape in Morrisville
review: I had an awesome time with my wife, sis-in-law, and friend! First time and it was enjoyable. We went through the Baker Street Green room and walked out being the only group since the room opening to get down to the last clue to get out. Would definitely do this again!!
